name: Dior couleurs
desc: Dior Diorshow 5 Couleurs palettes offer a wardrobe of eyeshadows, inspired by iconic Dior fashion pieces, with a range of finishes from matte to shimmer, metallic, and glitter. These palettes feature a creamy, comfortable, and long-wearing formula, infused with cornflower extract, and designed to deliver intense color payoff. The case itself is designed with a modern aesthetic, featuring the Dior signature and a clasp with the initials CD.

name: Perfect Match Foundation
image2: images/cosmetics/dior/Dior Backstage Face & Body Foundation details.jpg
desc: Dior Backstage Face & Body Foundation is a lightweight, buildable foundation that provides a natural-looking finish. It is designed to be worn on its own or under makeup for a flawless, airbrushed finish. The formula is infused with hyaluronic acid and glycer in to help retain moisture and provide a smooth, even texture. The foundation is available in 40 shades to suit a range of skin tones.

name: Dior Touch Face Powder
desc: Dior Touch Face Powder is a lightweight, oil-absorbing powder that helps to set makeup and control shine. It is designed to be worn on its own or over foundation for a smooth, even finish. The formula is infused with kaolin clay and talc to help absorb excess oil and reduce the appearance of pores. The powder is available in a range of shades to suit a range of skin tones.

name: Rouge Dior Forever Transfer-Proof Lipstick - Ultra Pigmented Matte - Bare-Lip Feel Comfort
desc: Dior Rouge Dior Forever Transfer-Proof Lipstick is a long-lasting, transfer-proof lipstick that provides a comfortable, bare-lip feel. It is designed to be worn on its own or over lip liner for a smooth, even finish. The formula is infused with hyal uronic acid and glycerin to help retain moisture and provide a smooth, even texture. The lipstick is available in a range of shades to suit a range of skin tones.

name: Dior lipglow
desc: Dior Mega Lash Mascara is a volumizing and lengthening mascara that helps to create a full, luscious lash look. It is designed to be worn on its own or over individual lashes for a dramatic, eye-catching finish. The formula is infused with keratin and biotin to help strengthen and condition lashes, while the brush is designed to coat lashes evenly and prevent clumping.

name: Mega Lash Mascara

name: Dior Eyeliner
desc: Dior eyeliners are designed to define and enhance the eyes with precision, offering a variety of formulas and finishes to suit different makeup styles. They come in liquid, pencil, and felt-tip options, including the waterproof Diorshow Stylo and Diorshow On Stage Liner, known for their long-lasting, intense color payoff and easy application.

name: Shimmer Glow Highlighter
desc: Dior Shimmer Glow Highlighter is a radiant, shimmering highlighter that adds a touch of light and dimension to the skin. It is designed to be worn on its own or over foundation for a natural, effortless finish. The formula is infused with hyaluronic acid and glycerin to help retain moisture and provide a smooth, even texture.
